<entry original="样本土壤：山峦R&M区域。
检测人员：" translated="Sample soil: Mountain R&M area.
Inspectors："/> <entry original="
检测结果：平均土壤有机质17.6g/kg-正常、全氮1.02g/kg-正常、速效磷22.6mg/kg-正常、稀有金属含量998mg/kg-异常。
主要稀有金属成分：钐-149、氪-137的含量占比为23.4﹪和70.1﹪ 备注：钐-149通常被称为【中子毒药】，是制作核反应堆控制棒的材料。通俗一点讲就是控制棒插进核反应堆的深浅能直接控制核反应堆的反应速度，因为中子毒药能吸收中子但自身不发生裂变从而对核裂变反应产生负影响。氪是单质气体为无色、无臭、无味的惰性气体，理论上说应该不会出现这种137同位素。但自从前一段时间爆出神秘绿色能量圈之后，这种氪-137经常被发现散落在其四周。
总结：这块区域具有核能开发价值。" translated="
Test results: Average soil organic matter 17.6g/kg-normal, total nitrogen 1.02g/kg-normal, quick-acting phosphorus 22.6mg/kg-normal, rare metal content 998 mg/kg-abnormal.
The main rare metal components: The content of samarium-149 and krypton-137 accounts for 23.4% and 70.1%. Note: Samarium-149 is often called [neutron poison] and is the material used to make control rods for nuclear reactors.In layman''s terms, the depth of the control rod inserted into the nuclear reactor can directly control the reaction speed of the nuclear reactor, because the neutron poison can absorb neutrons but does not fission itself, which has a negative impact on the nuclear fission reaction.Krypton is a elemental gas that is colorless, odorless, and odorless inert gas. In theory, this 137 isotope should not appear.But since the mysterious green energy circle exploded some time ago, this kind of krypton-137 has often been found scattered around it.
Summary: This area has the value of nuclear energy development."/>
